Here's the step-by-step solution:

\[
\begin{align*}
(n + 6.75) + 0.25 &= n + (6.75 + 0.25) \quad \text{(Associative Property)} \\
&= n + 7.00 \quad \text{(Add the numbers inside the parentheses)} \\
&= \boxed{n + 7}
\end{align*}
\]

